<lb ed="K" n="0954a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">懷感韻詩四</cb:mulu><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a0201" style="text-indent:0em"><l>醴泉平地湧</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a0206" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">夫瑞露天酒浪井醴泉皆帝王德合上玄恩<g ref="#CB31087"/>下土交泰
<lb ed="K" n="0954a03"/>致和以瑞於王者也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a0309" style="text-indent:0em"><l>神雀半空翔</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a0314" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">德動天鑒靈貺日臻所以神雀翔空
<lb ed="K" n="0954a04"/>丹鳳巢閣又豈假銜書表瑞化玉稱祥者哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a0418" style="text-indent:0em"><l>內廄縻龍驥</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a0423" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">天下有道
<lb ed="K" n="0954a05"/>王者尊賢則龍馬至今則尊師友行道德又何黃澤朱鬣之驥不縻於內廄焉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a0531" style="text-indent:0em"><l>瑤池
<lb ed="K" n="0954a06"/>浴鳳凰</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a0604" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">鳳凰以五色之文九包之狀來從丹<g ref="#CB08762"/>冾彼瑤池然後窺德於武王
<lb ed="K" n="0954a07"/>受圖於黃帝亦如賢明之相迴翔雞樹叶贊龍圖尓</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a0721" style="text-indent:0em"><l>五風恒作則</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a0726" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">書云知之
<lb ed="K" n="0954a08"/>曰明哲明哲實作則既哲且明先天不違煥乎時令以致時雍故得五風恒順四氣和通
<lb ed="K" n="0954a09"/>古者太平之代五日一風也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a0912" style="text-indent:0em"><l>十雨競悠颺</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a0917" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">太平之代十日一雨雨必
<lb ed="K" n="0954a10"/>以夜又管子曰五政苟時春雨乃來矣所以時雨沾潤萬物滋榮風雨無愆則聖人之化
<lb ed="K" n="0954a11"/>也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a1102" style="text-indent:0em"><l>閭巷皆歡恱</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a1107" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">周禮曰五家為比五比為閭謂人君之有道里巷之
<lb ed="K" n="0954a12"/>民皆恱也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a1205" style="text-indent:0em"><l>歌吹盡不妨</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a1210" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">風雨順序華夏懽娛歌吹之聲聞於閭巷者盖朝有
<lb ed="K" n="0954a13"/>多士家有餘粮擊壤皷腹以樂昇平也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a1316" style="text-indent:0em"><l>輕雲遙<g ref="#CB15468"/><g ref="#CB15468"/></l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a1321" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">史記云若煙非
<lb ed="K" n="0954a14"/>煙若雲非雲郁郁紛紛是謂慶雲彰王者之瑞</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a1419" style="text-indent:0em"><l>非霧起蒼蒼</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a1424" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">莊子曰天
<lb ed="K" n="0954a15"/>之蒼蒼其正色也以其遠而無所至極也所以祥煙時起非霧頻生以瑞於君也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a1532" style="text-indent:0em"><l>比
<lb ed="K" n="0954a16"/>屋千家樂</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a1605" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">惟德動天愛民若<note n="0954a1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">己【CB】，巳【麗】</note><app n="0954a1601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">己</lem><rdg wit="【麗】">巳</rdg></app>致之富壽育以慈仁既一物不失於所則
<lb ed="K" n="0954a17"/>千家之樂可聞也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a1708" style="text-indent:0em"><l>開扉眾顯昂</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a1713" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">沐浴皇化優游景風遵古而行不嚴
<lb ed="K" n="0954a18"/>而治閭里絕弊顯昂以居老子云安其居樂其俗也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a1821" style="text-indent:0em"><l>梅鋪村社白</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a1826" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">德既合於
<lb ed="K" n="0954a19"/>乹坤化<note n="0954a1901" resp="CBETA" type="add">己【CB】，巳【麗】</note><app n="0954a1901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">己</lem><rdg wit="【麗】">巳</rdg></app>被於草木寒梅自芳於村社發生不失於時冝者也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a1925" style="text-indent:0em"><l>柳映御街黃</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0954a20"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954a2001" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">柳條金線籠霽色於天街淑氣輕雲映朝霞於仙闕乃聖人應和風而覃雨露也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954a2032" style="text-indent:0em"><l>荷
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0954b" n="0954b"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0954b01"/>寵<g ref="#CB08221"/>藩閫</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b0105" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">寰瀛既定率土咸凞凡在功臣悉承寵渥或作鎮於會府或奉
<lb ed="K" n="0954b02"/>軄於雄藩如武王既罷干戈封太公於齊斯之謂也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b0221" style="text-indent:0em"><l>迎恩會<g ref="#CB22980"/>閶</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b0226" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">雨露
<lb ed="K" n="0954b03"/>既施於浹洽絲綸迎捧於天門盖賞罰之不虛表恩沾而有異</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b0325" style="text-indent:0em"><l>雕題來請吏</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0954b04"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b0401" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">雕題交趾航海來近請吏玉階則遠安邇肅之道昭矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b0422" style="text-indent:0em"><l>獫狁定賔王</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b0427" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">允叶
<lb ed="K" n="0954b05"/>聖運光被万方使辮髮羶食之徒咸遵聖化令獫狁戎羌之類悉以賓王</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b0529" style="text-indent:0em"><l>洞府籠
<lb ed="K" n="0954b06"/>仙署</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b0603" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">內宮禁苑如洞府以優遊殿閣輝華籠真仙之界署</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b0623" style="text-indent:0em"><l>靈椿壽帝鄉</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0954b07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b0701" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">躋民壽域其國樂哉與天齊休其道亨也億兆叶意祝乎靈椿率土之內無異仙鄉也</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0954b08"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b0801" style="text-indent:0em"><l>蠻夷<g ref="#CB08221"/>至德</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b0806" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">皇天無親惟德是輔萬方向化率土來王蹈舞彤<g ref="#CB00527"/>歡呼
<lb ed="K" n="0954b09"/>玉殿被髮文身之士茹毛飲血之徒駈犀象以輸賝涉梯航而献贄<g ref="#CB22958"/>茲異域錫賚覃恩
<lb ed="K" n="0954b10"/>矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b1002" style="text-indent:0em"><l>制度法成湯</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b1007" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">聖人御宇法彼上玄翼翼小心巍巍大度<g ref="#CB07560"/>開三靣佉貸
<lb ed="K" n="0954b11"/>五刑<g ref="#CB22958"/>物恤人眚災肆赦</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b1111" style="text-indent:0em"><l>曲沼垂鈎餌</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b1116" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">御水縈紆傍分曲沼芙蕖蔟岸蘋藻
<lb ed="K" n="0954b12"/>陵波手執絲綸鈎垂香餌表一人之無事知四海之晏然遊幸臨流可以怡懷矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b1232" style="text-indent:0em"><l>清
<lb ed="K" n="0954b13"/>波躍鯉魴</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b1305" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">清波碧沼沃潤瑤池雨霽深沉萍浮魚戲詩云豈其食魚必河之魴</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0954b14"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b1401" style="text-indent:0em"><l>晴軒流月影</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b1406" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">名踰長樂義勝忘憂功麗形軒巧殊紫柱金鋪動色藻<g ref="#CB12561"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0954b15"/>飛雲月觸簷楹風生窓牖古詩云安寢北堂上明月入我牖照之有餘暉攪之不盈乎</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0954b16"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b1601" style="text-indent:0em"><l>踈檻透清光</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b1606" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">花敷欄檻水暎林亭靜曒銀蟾光舒玉殿矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b1623" style="text-indent:0em"><l>武庫森
<lb ed="K" n="0954b17"/>戈<g ref="#CB02455"/></l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b1703" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">威儀五法制度九章龍虵之氣勢逶迤日月之光輝聳朗戈矛耀雪戟槊植林
<lb ed="K" n="0954b18"/>保人定功俻而不用矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b1810" style="text-indent:0em"><l>軍容尚繡裝</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b1815" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">六衛之眾禁旅之兵衣綺繡之裝振
<lb ed="K" n="0954b19"/>貔虎之勢行如曳錦住若攢花煥赫軍容斯為盛矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b1921" style="text-indent:0em"><l>觸邪嚴獬豸</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b1926" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline"><g ref="#CB22026"/>茨土階
<lb ed="K" n="0954b20"/>慈儉之德至矣獬豸蓂莢政理之道致矣故得姦邪鷁退忠讜鴞立今國家侔唐堯之風
<lb ed="K" n="0954b21"/>雖繡衣豸冠且無邪可觸矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954b2112" style="text-indent:0em"><l>啟悵列星郎</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954b2117" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">漢書云郎官上應列宿故
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0954c" n="0954c"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0954c01"/>當其位必稱其軄所以啟金閭玉堂以延之建蘭臺粉署以處之俾潤色皇猷發揮儒墨
<lb ed="K" n="0954c02"/>也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c0202" style="text-indent:0em"><l>寓目忻時泰</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c0207" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">聖人萬機之外矚時泰以民康迴顧怡懷念蒼生之
<lb ed="K" n="0954c03"/>有福也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c0304" style="text-indent:0em"><l>怡情喜歲穰</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c0309" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">歲時既稔國用益充寬宵旰之情怡然游處也</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0954c04"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c0401" style="text-indent:0em"><l>和羹思鼎鼐</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c0406" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">亦猶庶政之事委以台輔簡而成治故高宗命傳說
<lb ed="K" n="0954c05"/>云若作和羹用尓作塩梅也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c0512" style="text-indent:0em"><l>奏樂飲瓊漿</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c0517" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">九成之樂奏而非荒也千
<lb ed="K" n="0954c06"/>鍾之酒飲而非乱也盖聽政之餘逍遙大<g ref="#CB00527"/>群臣高會矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c0623" style="text-indent:0em"><l>解凍興東作</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0954c07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c0701" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">立春之日東風解凍皇帝布農事於東郊祈五穀於上帝親載耒耜躬耕籍田大興東作
<lb ed="K" n="0954c08"/>也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c0802" style="text-indent:0em"><l>瞻雲望北邙</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c0807" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">東洛之北有邙山宮闕相連雲樹交映今聖人安天
<lb ed="K" n="0954c09"/>下立太平故於萬機之餘而瞻望也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c0915" style="text-indent:0em"><l>輕傜寬賦稅</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c0920" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">車書混同天地交泰
<lb ed="K" n="0954c10"/>四方無事萬物义寧克念田疇誡重<g ref="#CB00866"/>而恱康時也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c1021" style="text-indent:0em"><l>美景度炎涼</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c1026" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">皇居壯麗
<lb ed="K" n="0954c11"/>上體環極美景良辰賞心樂事瓊林玉榭瑞露仙禽端拱穆清履四時之和平</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c1131" style="text-indent:0em"><l>擅武施
<lb ed="K" n="0954c12"/>三令</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c1203" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">設官分軄體道乘時禮樂征伐出自於天子五申三令擅委於謀臣垂衣裳而天下
<lb ed="K" n="0954c13"/>治也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c1303" style="text-indent:0em"><l>崇儒順五常</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c1308" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">五行天之用五常人之法應天順人隨時設教故崇於大
<lb ed="K" n="0954c14"/>學置於蘭省取四科之士修五教之道播仁聖之風文武各得分其用矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c1429" style="text-indent:0em"><l>直誠無
<lb ed="K" n="0954c15"/>妬忌</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c1503" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">君明於上臣忠於下舉事務直納言無咈大臣良輔皆有賢故諂侫不生
<lb ed="K" n="0954c16"/>於國矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c1604" style="text-indent:0em"><l>舉步蘊行藏</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c1609" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">濟濟多士元后寧之動合典章靜苻玄化羽儀
<lb ed="K" n="0954c17"/>王道無怠肅恭者哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c1709" style="text-indent:0em"><l>春滿皇州麗</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c1714" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">居中得正運化調元和氣滂流齊光
<lb ed="K" n="0954c18"/>品物皇都嘉麗何莫由斯亦萬國之歡心也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c1818" style="text-indent:0em"><l>花繁上苑芳</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c1823" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">天道亨利園花
<lb ed="K" n="0954c19"/>發滋欝馥鮮明清芬交蔭本枝百世貞實萬年蕃盛之理也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c1924" style="text-indent:0em"><l>閑情資覆
<lb ed="K" n="0954c20"/>燾</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c2002" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">皇綱序而睿思閑淳風扇而思波洽資法天法地之政施以覆以燾之仁<g ref="#CB00982"/>子
<lb ed="K" n="0954c21"/>云明王之功盖天下</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0954c2109" style="text-indent:0em"><l>有智靜関防</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0954c2114" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">智以遊刃方機德以柔服四海神謀
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0955a" n="0955a"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0955a01"/>密運以靜関防故得邊徼無虞物不失所者也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a0119" style="text-indent:0em"><l>敗虜<g ref="#CB13378"/>車帳</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a0124" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">王者順彼
<lb ed="K" n="0955a02"/>天時出師以律醜虜之眾無畏威故奔走而<g ref="#CB13378"/>弃車悵也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a0223" style="text-indent:0em"><l>戎渠<g ref="#CB15164"/>耳璫</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955a03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a0301" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">西戎風俗皆餙以耳璫抑亦稟乎天威惟命是聽故戎師魁渠嚴其餙裝盡朝於聖化矣</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955a04"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a0401" style="text-indent:0em"><l>鷰歸知社近</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a0406" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">且化遐被物得其冝如彼鷰知時而歸矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a0422" style="text-indent:0em"><l><g ref="#CB10265"/>化
<lb ed="K" n="0955a05"/>夢猶<g ref="#CB00982"/></l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a0504" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline"><g ref="#CB00982"/>周夢中身化為<g ref="#CB10265"/>斯湏一夢翱翔百年誰知此身曾不遷易</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a0528" style="text-indent:0em"><l>聚
<lb ed="K" n="0955a06"/>落安<g ref="#CB00932"/>庶</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a0605" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">眾人所居名曰聚落聚落既靜烏無夜啼日出而作開物成務
<lb ed="K" n="0955a07"/>務安黎庶者也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a0707" style="text-indent:0em"><l>通才莅事強</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a0712" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">所任賢士慎選通才共治邦家典御天下
<lb ed="K" n="0955a08"/>舉直措抂臨莅無偏撫察之間必見強明者矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a0819" style="text-indent:0em"><l>封陲寬蕩蕩</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a0824" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">富有四海
<lb ed="K" n="0955a09"/>威臨萬邦盡歸大化之風各奉文明之德故封陲蕩蕩寰宇昭昭也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a0927" style="text-indent:0em"><l>生植茂牂
<lb ed="K" n="0955a10"/>牂</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a1002" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">牂牂乃茂盛之<g ref="#CB15032"/>此意言動植草木之蕃滋茂育也此乃聖人澤周萬物皆遂生發
<lb ed="K" n="0955a11"/>矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a1102" style="text-indent:0em"><l>壟畒堆紅腐</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a1107" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline"><note n="0955a1101" resp="CBETA" type="add">豐【CB】，豊【麗】</note><app n="0955a1101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">豐</lem><rdg wit="【麗】">豊</rdg></app>年上瑞稔歲方登南畝東臯農夫樂唱倉箱堆積
<lb ed="K" n="0955a12"/>而紅腐黍稷常被於田疇</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a1211" style="text-indent:0em"><l>桒榆勝綠楊</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a1216" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">民無墯業咸務耕織故桒榆之
<lb ed="K" n="0955a13"/>利<g ref="#CB12752"/>深楊柳之材益寡也史記云齊魯之間有千畒桒比千戶侯也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a1327" style="text-indent:0em"><l>書紳無彼
<lb ed="K" n="0955a14"/>此</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a1402" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">紳者大帶也夫子門人子張聞善言而書諸紳今則愛人乘誨心無彼此矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a1431" style="text-indent:0em"><l>揖
<lb ed="K" n="0955a15"/>讓盡鏗鏘</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a1505" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">先人後巳行者讓路則君臣父子盡懷濟濟之儀各振鏘鏘之
<lb ed="K" n="0955a16"/><g ref="#CB15032"/></note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a1602" style="text-indent:0em"><l>世反純和理</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a1607" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">進德修業乃可大可久故好古<g ref="#CB13415"/>雅去彼取此則去耆慾
<lb ed="K" n="0955a17"/>之心行淳和之理而化于世也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a1713" style="text-indent:0em"><l>官清離賄贓</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a1718" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">設官分爵務在清廉既明
<lb ed="K" n="0955a18"/>為政之風盡善化人之法刑無枉濫獄難賄贓故比戶之民自樂也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a1827" style="text-indent:0em"><l>平原先畎
<lb ed="K" n="0955a19"/>澮</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a1902" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">爾雅云廣平曰原釋名云引水田會處曰畎澮欲平於原隰先治於畎澮所謂大道
<lb ed="K" n="0955a20"/>妒<g ref="#CB10614"/>無不坦途亦猶一統寰區萬方歸化王道蕩蕩更無殊俗者焉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955a2027" style="text-indent:0em"><l>拒轍信螗
<lb ed="K" n="0955a21"/>蜋</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955a2102" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">韓詩外傳曰宋<g ref="#CB00982"/>公出有螗蜋拒於轍下公曰彼不量力也大轍若當於得勢小蟲
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0955b" n="0955b"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0955b01"/>住拒於當衢驟轂飛輸寧阻于康莊者矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0117" style="text-indent:0em"><l>恬淡無高下</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b0122" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">恬淡之性性本天然
<lb ed="K" n="0955b02"/>高下無殊遠近何異千變萬化不能傾動焉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0218" style="text-indent:0em"><l>因緣任短長</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b0223" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">作如是因有如
<lb ed="K" n="0955b03"/>是緣因緣一生則長短顯晦之道任真而<note n="0955b0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【麗】</note><app n="0955b0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【麗】">巳</rdg></app></note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0318" style="text-indent:0em"><l>幽禽捿澗谷</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b0323" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">仁反飛走則澗
<lb ed="K" n="0955b04"/>谷之幽禽隨時任性而自樂也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0413" style="text-indent:0em"><l>寒<g ref="#CB13465"/>度瀟湘</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b0418" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">避矰繳以銜蘆度瀟湘而乘月
<lb ed="K" n="0955b05"/>來賔應<g ref="#CB07419"/>随陽得時</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0509" style="text-indent:0em"><l>野逈胡塵滅</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b0514" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">折衝<g ref="#CB22021"/>俎醜類遁逃黃塵既息於邊
<lb ed="K" n="0955b06"/>陲赤子盡歸於聖化</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0609" style="text-indent:0em"><l>年<note n="0955b0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">豐【CB】，豊【麗】</note><app n="0955b0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">豐</lem><rdg wit="【麗】">豊</rdg></app>積貸粮</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b0614" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">貸者借也年饑則散太倉之栗借民
<lb ed="K" n="0955b07"/>充食方今東作西成嘉禾再稻民有餘食則貸糧<g ref="#CB00036"/>而無用也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0725" style="text-indent:0em"><l>端珪朝太極</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955b08"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b0801" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">天下無事則聖人端珪而御正殿百辟朝會如星拱辰太極殿名也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0827" style="text-indent:0em"><l>道化鎮中
<lb ed="K" n="0955b09"/>央</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b0902" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">以堯舜無為之道底定中華自然拱手垂衣而化成天下</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b0924" style="text-indent:0em"><l>悖亂知迷惑</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955b10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1001" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">百獸尚能率舞為臣曷昧變通而乃悖戾亂常自貽伊戚如四凶之類豈非迷惑者<g ref="#CB27329"/></note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955b11"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1101" style="text-indent:0em"><l>修持免咎殃</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1106" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">修仁秉義持謙戒盈不唯遠害全身可以慶延長世</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1126" style="text-indent:0em"><l>漁樵
<lb ed="K" n="0955b12"/>忻樂業</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1204" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">或放志煙波或長歌巖野優游自得誰知帝恩如鑿井耕田之叟矣</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955b13"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1301" style="text-indent:0em"><l>吳越<g ref="#CB28575"/>交商</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1306" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">溥天之下莫非王土吳越之商徃來無阻</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1322" style="text-indent:0em"><l>禁暴窮
<lb ed="K" n="0955b14"/>兵筞</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1403" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">禁戢暴黨湏善兵機刑期無刑盖不獲<note n="0955b1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【麗】</note><app n="0955b1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【麗】">巳</rdg></app>是以自古帝王皆乃文乃武</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1430" style="text-indent:0em"><l>尊
<lb ed="K" n="0955b15"/>賢養國庠</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1505" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">所貿惟賢為國之本開庠進善長育英才斯乃帝王之恒式爾</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955b16"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1601" style="text-indent:0em"><l>田多論萬頃</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1606" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">風雨以時大甲多稼登高望遠如雲藹然萬頃之多舉一
<lb ed="K" n="0955b17"/>隅爾</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1703" style="text-indent:0em"><l>食足重千箱</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1708" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">我田既咸農夫之慶既種既戒如茨如梁乃求千斯
<lb ed="K" n="0955b18"/>倉以處之萬斯箱以載之</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1811" style="text-indent:0em"><l>堯聖何儔疋</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b1816" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">光被四海恊和萬邦以欽明而
<lb ed="K" n="0955b19"/>平章百姓以俊德而親睦九族其明如日其仁如天五帝<note n="0955b1901" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【麗】</note><app n="0955b1901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【麗】">巳</rdg></app>還孰能為疋</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b1929" style="text-indent:0em"><l>舜聦豈
<lb ed="K" n="0955b20"/>等量</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955b2003" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">聽明曰聦彰乎四達若藥之言可進如簧之語難伸是以賢有大來人無
<lb ed="K" n="0955b21"/>所失民雖受賜莫得而稱如人終日戴天而不知天之高也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955b2124" style="text-indent:0em"><l>守文明肅晏</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0955c" n="0955c"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0955c01"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c0101" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">五典克從九功惟敘萬邦肅穆四海晏康則聖文之所被矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c0124" style="text-indent:0em"><l>息戰弭旗搶</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955c02"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c0201" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">七德備彰四方無<g ref="#CB07532"/>干戈倒載牛馬<g ref="#CB09109"/>閑則神武之所被矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c0224" style="text-indent:0em"><l>下俚饒分謗</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955c03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c0301" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">下民之愚不知賦分祁寒暑雨惟日怨咨豈知簞食瓢飲而樂在其中者哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c0330" style="text-indent:0em"><l>中庸
<lb ed="K" n="0955c04"/>在審詳</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c0404" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">中庸之人可以語上見不賢而自省聞大道以若存動必三思庶無
<lb ed="K" n="0955c05"/>二過</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c0503" style="text-indent:0em"><l>掖<g ref="#CB00527"/>霞燦燦</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c0508" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">金屋黃闈掖<g ref="#CB00527"/>紫禁不壯不麗何以威遠來柔故得
<lb ed="K" n="0955c06"/>綺霞燦燦而朝籠景風悠悠而夕起盖無為道著不宰功成於馬游處不其樂哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c0632" style="text-indent:0em"><l>宮
<lb ed="K" n="0955c07"/>沼浪泱泱</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c0705" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">觀夫宮沼之設見聖人之用心矣欲使皇澤流而不壅天波注
<lb ed="K" n="0955c08"/>而不竭其或春之朝雨之霽晴波澄澈浮仙花於九重寒浪浟瀜泛湛恩於萬里是知睿
<lb ed="K" n="0955c09"/>藻寄情邈然無際矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c0909" style="text-indent:0em"><l>鵬翥三清路</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c0914" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">騰翥遠者唯大鵬焉九萬為程六月
<lb ed="K" n="0955c10"/>一息亦猶士韞命世之才懷致治之道龍躍天衢振翼雲漢望三清之路豈為遠哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c1033" style="text-indent:0em"><l>鴻
<lb ed="K" n="0955c11"/>排一字行</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c1105" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">振鷺在<g ref="#CB00527"/>鴛鴻成列曉近金砌寒趍玉<g ref="#CB29323"/>既一字以為行乃百
<lb ed="K" n="0955c12"/>拜而稱壽矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c1206" style="text-indent:0em"><l>飛書搜草澤</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c1211" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">月令季春之月開府庫出幣帛周天下勉
<lb ed="K" n="0955c13"/>諸侯聘名士逮于幽隱復以弓旌招納蒱帛徵命<g ref="#CB07419"/>以<g ref="#CB00527"/>燎待以前席不却九九之流况
<lb ed="K" n="0955c14"/>乎傳巖渭濵之叟哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c1409" style="text-indent:0em"><l>恤物勸農桒</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c1414" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">君天下者躬稼以供粢盛所以致孝
<lb ed="K" n="0955c15"/>也勸穡以足百姓所以固本也繇是天子降靈壇撫御耦游場染屨洪縻在手三推而舍
<lb ed="K" n="0955c16"/>庶人終畒欲使九土之冝四民之務五穀登而百神受享也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c1624" style="text-indent:0em"><l>報應隨名在</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0955c17"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c1701" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">善惡之報世代之人皆耳目之所知故不假一二而言也為善所以降福作<g ref="#CB08891"/>由是招禍
<lb ed="K" n="0955c18"/>縱三教雖異且一轍同歸故報應隨形如影響矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c1820" style="text-indent:0em"><l>施為善否臧</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c1825" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">福善禍淫
<lb ed="K" n="0955c19"/>之道既著徵<g ref="#CB08891"/>勸善之理攸冝然於施張舉措賞罰取捨之間審於臨事遵彼爯思儻否
<lb ed="K" n="0955c20"/>咸不差則悔吝何有仲<g ref="#CB00112"/>云造次必於是顛沛必於是</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0955c2022" style="text-indent:0em"><l>天高歸宇內</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0955c2027" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">天之
<lb ed="K" n="0955c21"/>象也雖高天之道也弗遠惟天陰隲下民使有常生之資者莫不全歸我皇區宇之內也</note>。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0956a" n="0956a"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0956a01"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0956a0101" style="text-indent:0em"><l>糓稔絕飛蝗</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0956a0106" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">夫厚生之本八政何先八政之中惟食命<g ref="#CB08764"/>方今五行無
<lb ed="K" n="0956a02"/>易百糓用成行發<g ref="#CB09109"/>微時推稔歲且蠈<g ref="#CB07530"/>螟蟄之類尚不為蠹況彼飛蝗而為患乎<g ref="#CB27329"/></note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0956a03"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0956a0301" style="text-indent:0em"><l>玩好空臺榭</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0956a0306" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">不寶遠物無所玩好故臺榭多空矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0956a0320" style="text-indent:0em"><l>賢明<g ref="#CB13415"/>陸
<lb ed="K" n="0956a04"/>堂</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0956a0402" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">賢明在上睿哲居尊獨断萬機<g ref="#CB12752"/>新盛德雖<g ref="#CB13415"/>陸之妙何有於我哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0956a0428" style="text-indent:0em"><l>是非
<lb ed="K" n="0956a05"/>難可究</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0956a0504" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">愛<g ref="#CB08891"/>相紛是非相糺非夫量窮世表識動機先則無以究也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0956a0527" style="text-indent:0em"><l>安
<lb ed="K" n="0956a06"/>健免<g ref="#CB28360"/>尫</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0956a0605" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">惟天所以勸人用五福一曰壽二曰富三曰康寧四曰攸
<lb ed="K" n="0956a07"/>好德五曰考終命故形不羸而<g ref="#CB15032"/>不尫也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0956a0717" style="text-indent:0em"><l>立譽湏兢慎</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0956a0722" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">流譽垂千載之
<lb ed="K" n="0956a08"/>下成功高百代之前斯乃帝王之能事也兢兢慎之至矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0956a0823" style="text-indent:0em"><l><g ref="#CB07448"/>蒙出定房</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0956a09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0956a0901" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">定以不亂為性一真云寂萬法斯如故稱定也夫究治之本則<g ref="#CB07448"/><g ref="#CB07448"/>然得其體也蒙蒙然
<lb ed="K" n="0956a10"/>養其用也從是而論猶僧出定動兮無撓靜也寧拘</note>。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0956a11"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="29"><cb:jhead>御製秘藏詮懷感一百韻詩卷第二十九</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="K" n="0956a12"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pK35p0956a1201" style="margin-left:1em">丁未歲高麗國大藏都監奉
<lb ed="K" n="0956a13" type="honorific"/><g ref="#CB30072"/>雕造</p></cb:div>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>